    "freq": 4,
    "passage": "Directions: Read the following passage and choose the best answer for items 1-5.\n\nIn the past, people had to go to a shop to buy what they needed. Today, many people shop online using their phones or computers. Online shopping has become very popular because it is convenient.\n\nThere are many good things about shopping online. You can buy products at any time, even late at night. You do not have to travel or wait in long lines. It is also easy to compare prices from different shops before you decide to buy.\n\nHowever, online shopping also has some bad sides. You cannot touch or try the product before it arrives, so it may not be what you expected. Sometimes the product takes a long time to be delivered. There is also a risk that dishonest sellers may cheat buyers.\n\nTo shop safely online, you should buy from shops that have good reviews and never share your password with anyone."
